PrecisAuthority (a) to sell a surplus strip of SAINT-HUBERT AIRPORT grounds to the City of SAINT-HUBERT for the purposes of the construction of Clairevue Boulevard, (b) to grant surface rights and attendant easements to the City for the installation, operation, etc., of water and sewer works on airport grounds, and (c) to grant surface rights and attendant easements to the City of SAINT-BRUNO-DE-MONTARVILLE for similar purposes.
